[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:20,460 --> 00:01:28,580
Arsenal Military Academy

3
00:01:28,860 --> 00:01:31,580
Episode 05

4
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:35,840
I heard a few days ago,

5
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,440
when Ms. Qu was in Club Paramo,

6
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:40,039
she almost got abducted.

7
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,440
We're in troubled times now.

8
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,080
Bandits are rampant.

9
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,600
You should be more careful

10
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:48,400
when going outside.

11
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:55,880
Tingbai will protect me.

12
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,200
Don't worry.

13
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,250
Be careful when you go outside.

14
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,320
Or just stay at home if possible.

15
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:28,600
I can send more bodyguards to protect you.

16
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,760
Don't listen to him.

17
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,360
If he really wanted to hurt me,

18
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,890
he wouldn't say it out loud.

19
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,240
Right now,

20
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,160
the Japanese are in power.

21
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,400
No one dares to fight

22
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:40,800
against them except you.

23
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,140
You should be careful.

24
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,600
I'll fight against them if I have to.

25
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,720
But I will never bow and scrape to the Japanese

26
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:49,980
not in a million years.

27
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,600
What?

28
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,720
You looked like an adult when you were a kid.

29
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,840
How come you're so childish now?

30
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,280
I'm not childish.

31
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,220
You wouldn't understand.

32
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,560
Listen,

33
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,880
just take good care of yourself,

34
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,080
okay?

35
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,079
Stop it!

36
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,730
Don't touch my head.

37
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,490
So annoying!

38
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:22,200
Don't forget to dance with me later.

39
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,079
We'll see.

40
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,160
Miss,

41
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,800
can you do me a favor?

42
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,850
Please tell the man outside

43
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,360
that I need more time.

44
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,079
Don't wait for me.

45
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:51,680
OK.

46
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:52,840
Thank you.

47
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,080
He said it's OK,

48
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,160
and he isn't in a hurry.

49
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,360
You can take your time.

50
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:11,040
He will take you to the lounge for makeup after you finish.

51
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:11,800
Alright,

52
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,680
thank you.

53
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,130
Sure. You can continue.

54
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:21,510
Chairman,

55
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:23,640
should we teach Shen Tingbai

56
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:24,680
a lesson?

57
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:28,320
The Shens have run business in Shunyuan

58
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,000
for generations.

59
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:34,320
Shen Tingbai is well connected.

60
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,640
We can't mess with him for now.

61
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,450
Then we can start

62
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,810
with the people related to him.

63
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,159
Obviously,

64
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,650
he cares about that woman a lot.

65
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:52,560
Act with caution.

66
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,650
Don't make a huge scene.

67
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:58,040
If the military steps in,

68
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,200
the benefit

69
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,640
won't belong to us totally.

70
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,400
It's such an honor

71
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,560
to have the Mayor and

72
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,760
Vice Minister Gu here.

73
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,540
Don't be so polite.

74
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,400
Your father and I go way back.

75
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,160
I'm also gratified to see

76
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:19,480
you grow up.

77
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,400
Like father, like son.

78
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,680
Mr. Shen is so lucky to have a son like you

79
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,740
who can take over the family business

80
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,400
so that he can retire at an early age.

81
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:32,120
We do envy him.

82
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,360
Mr. Gu's son

83
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:36,800
is outstanding.

84
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,320
Everyone's known him

85
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,090
shortly after he came here.

86
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,520
Mr. Gu,

87
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,720
Yanzhen is in Shunyuan, too?

88
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,220
Why didn't you mention it?

89
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,880
Let's not waste time

90
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,280
talking about that brat.

91
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,600
Youngsters

92
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,040
are always naughty.

93
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,120
As long as we educate them well,

94
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,320
they'll be fine.

95
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,120
I hope so.

96
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,600
Excuse me for a while.

97
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,680
Alright.

98
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,320
Dad,

99
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:27,520
you said that the Shens and us are friends,

100
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,960
but why haven't I met him before?

101
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,080
You grew up in Peking

102
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,560
and went to Britain later.

103
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,560
It's normal that you don't know him.

104
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:37,970
He is the eldest son of your Uncle Shen.

105
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:40,920
Well,

106
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:44,200
don't you remember Uncle Shen

107
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,680
who gave you the mink?

108
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,240
I remember.

109
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,000
One year during the Spring Festival,

110
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,360
Uncle Shen came to visit and brought presents.

111
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:53,280
He gave my mom

112
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,360
a white mink coat.

113
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:57,080
Then he asked me what I wanted.

114
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,800
I said I wanted a living mink.

115
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:01,320
Then the next year,

116
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,980
he really came and gave me one.

117
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:07,720
I was afraid that it would get cold,

118
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,960
so I put it on the cage

119
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,200
beside the stove,

120
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,960
and cover it with thick cotton.

121
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,640
Then the mink died shortly after that.

122
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,120
If you like it,

123
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:21,720
I can have my people send you another one.

124
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,240
Really?

125
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,760
I just returned home.

126
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,560
I don't know anybody

127
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,360
or have any friends, either.

128
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,360
Later on,

129
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,080
you can ask me for the first dance

130
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:36,840
so that

131
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:37,770
we can be friends

132
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,770
and then I can accept your gift.

133
00:07:43,520 --> 00:07:44,680
What's wrong?

134
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,760
You're a gentleman,

135
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,240
I'm a lady,

136
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,280
so you should obey my order.

137
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,540
You can't turn me down.

138
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,680
And,

139
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:56,720
it's rude to refuse a lady.

140
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,640
You won't do that,

141
00:07:58,880 --> 00:07:59,440
right?

142
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,280
I don't know if I

143
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,680
have the honor to

144
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,960
invite Ms. Bai for a dance?

145
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,520
Sure.

146
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:00,280
Mr. Shen and Ms. Bai

147
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,340
really look like a perfect match.

148
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,720
They just like

149
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,600
the people from a painting.

150
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:09,200
She is the Mayor's daughter,

151
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,440
who is beyond commoners.

152
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,640
Ms. Du,

153
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,730
men like your cousin with such appearance

154
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,880
and family status,

155
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,120
can only be matched by Ms. Bai.

156
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,280
Others are

157
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,880
laughing stocks.

158
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,640
Sadly, there are so many people

159
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,690
who overestimate themselves.

160
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,680
Ms. Qu,

161
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,200
do I have the honor

162
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:08,920
to invite you for a dance?

163
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:03,730
Are you jealous?

164
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:04,880
Of whom?

165
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,520
Shen Tingbai.

166
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,400
He's pursuing me,

167
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,730
not the other way round.

168
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:15,680
Have you never fallen in love with anyone?

169
00:11:15,680 --> 00:11:16,240
No.

170
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,360
And you?

171
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,600
Well,

172
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:22,680
me either.

173
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,560
Then we're even.

174
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,730
I helped you out,

175
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:37,720
and please don't bother me anymore.

176
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,520
Bother?

177
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,720
Why do I need to bother you?

178
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,160
Gu Yanzhen,

179
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,400
this isn't over!

180
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,170
You are so petty.

181
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,730
Yeah, you pissed off the wrong one.

182
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,320
Great Bravo!

183
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:55,920
Nice.

184
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:57,040
Excellent.

185
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:16,280
Ms. Xie.

186
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:17,560
Ms. Xie!

187
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,040
Sorry, I'm sorry.

188
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:56,160
I heard that

189
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:58,090
Mr. Shen's youngest son

190
00:12:58,520 --> 00:12:59,780
is at the Academy, too.

191
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,800
He spoke on and on about that

192
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:05,970
the whole night.

193
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,850
Now the whole world knows that.

194
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,840
The two sons of Mr. Shen,

195
00:13:12,040 --> 00:13:13,600
one is a patriotic businessman,

196
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:16,120
the other is a passionate officer.

197
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,880
So great.

198
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,000
Dad,

199
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,960
don't try to test me.

200
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,960
There is no need

201
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,840
to joke around in front of me.

202
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,480
How is the relationship between you two?

203
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,280
So-so.

204
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,160
Neither have we talked,

205
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,220
nor have we fought.

206
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,280
Remember,

207
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,400
keep a distance from him.

208
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:38,600
The Shens have crossed the line.

209
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:40,540
If they go on like this,

210
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:43,010
they'll get into trouble sooner or later.

211
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,280
Dad,

212
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:47,880
are there still decent people in your eyes?

213
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:53,100
I don't care about others,

214
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:54,240
but you're my son,

215
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,140
of course I care about you.

216
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,880
It's OK to make small mistakes,

217
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:00,400
but you should know

218
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,890
what's right and wrong.

219
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,840
I don't need you to grace our family,

220
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:07,280
but don't cause trouble at least.

221
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,410
Right and wrong?

222
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,720
Dad, you think too much of yourself.

223
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,600
Whether it's right or wrong

224
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,520
is not your call nowadays.

225
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,530
But don't worry,

226
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:21,440
I'm not interested in these things.

227
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:44,840
Zhao,

228
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:45,600
come with me.

229
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,160
Yes.

230
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:55,760
Young master,

231
00:14:58,080 --> 00:14:59,280
with all due respect,

232
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:02,800
you shouldn't talk to your father like this.

233
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:04,120
Actually,

234
00:15:04,120 --> 00:15:05,920
Mr. Gu has been upset these days.

235
00:15:06,280 --> 00:15:08,520
The Japanese are sending more troops to Feng'an.

236
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:10,980
Although he is the Vice Governor of Feng'an,

237
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:13,200
he has no troops

238
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,680
or money in his hands.

239
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,880
Zhang Xihou, Bai Peiyong,

240
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:18,160
and people like them

241
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:19,620
all have evil intentions,

242
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:21,410
let alone those above them.

243
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:23,920
The military is also in disarray.

244
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:25,480
And the students

245
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,560
always launch marches

246
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:29,740
and petitions.

247
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:31,900
Mr. Gu hasn't slept well for days.

248
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:32,840
Look,

249
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:34,980
you've finally come back,

250
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,680
please don't upset him more.

251
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:38,880
Mr. Zhao,

252
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,490
who taught you to say these?

253
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:42,520
Pretty classy.

254
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,000
No one taught me.

255
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:45,970
The more you see,

256
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,600
the more you understand.

257
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,160
Mr. Gu's life isn't easy.

258
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,820
Please be considerate of him.

259
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:52,960
Fine, I got it.

260
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,620
Wait, Mr. Zhao,

261
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:59,050
I need you to check something for me

262
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:00,280
that

263
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:03,740
if there was a Ms. Xie in Shen's party tonight

264
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,120
who was around eighteen

265
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:08,640
and might've

266
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,520
come with her family.

267
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:13,640
OK.

268
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:16,100
I'll let you know as soon as I have the result.

269
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:37,160
Here.

270
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,520
Hi.

271
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:48,420
Take off your clothes.

272
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,280
What?

273
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,240
It is broken.

274
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:53,690
Let me stitch it for you.

275
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:54,810
That's fine.

276
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,300
Take it off.

277
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:08,760
Xiaojun,

278
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,010
bring me the sewing box.

279
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:12,040
OK.

280
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,530
The noodles smell good.

281
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:21,109
The Academy you work at

282
00:17:22,349 --> 00:17:23,589
let their staff walk around

283
00:17:23,589 --> 00:17:25,040
with holes in their clothes?

284
00:17:25,040 --> 00:17:27,000
The salary they pay

285
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:28,840
isn't enough for me to drink.

286
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:31,970
If they pay you more,

287
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:33,720
you can even

288
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:35,720
clear out a liquor store.

289
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,720
I made a suit for you.

290
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,610
You can try it later.

291
00:17:47,120 --> 00:17:49,120
I can fix it if it doesn't fit you.

292
00:17:49,560 --> 00:17:50,720
Why did you make it?

293
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,000
I don't even have

294
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:53,960
