00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:51,330
Why are you here?

592
00:39:51,520 --> 00:39:52,850
I've finally found you.

593
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:54,080
Go away.

594
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,880
You don't know how dangerous it was.

595
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:57,000
There were gunshots everywhere.

596
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,520
And I got separated from Zhu Yanlin.

597
00:39:58,520 --> 00:39:59,320
I thought I'd never see my dad again.

598
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:00,250
Enough, enough.

599
00:40:00,740 --> 00:40:01,670
Man up, will you?

600
00:40:04,040 --> 00:40:05,040
Wait! Wait for me!

601
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:42,660
Gu Yanzhen!

602
00:40:43,640 --> 00:40:44,120
Gu,

603
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:45,800
Gu Yanzhen!

604
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,520
Gu Yanzhen!

605
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,120
Gu Yanzhen!

606
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,160
Does it hurt?

607
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,360
You said

608
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:02,930
someone pushed you off.

609
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,610
Did you see his face?

610
00:41:08,280 --> 00:41:09,920
I passed out after I

611
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:11,160
fell into that pit.

612
00:41:11,160 --> 00:41:12,420
I didn't see anything.

613
00:41:16,160 --> 00:41:18,560
You said there were others in the forest.

614
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:20,370
Maybe one of them did it.

615
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,840
But why didn't he kill you

616
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:26,680
or catch you?

617
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:30,560
Maybe

618
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:31,740
it was one of us.

619
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:33,080
One of us?

620
00:41:35,520 --> 00:41:36,920
Everything is possible.

621
00:41:37,840 --> 00:41:39,560
One should never intend to harm others,

622
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:41,160
but should always guard against the harm others might do to him.

623
00:41:41,160 --> 00:41:42,420
Be careful from now on.

624
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:48,460
You're quite skilled at dressing the wound.

625
00:41:48,600 --> 00:41:49,480
Have you learned it?

626
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:50,880
I used to be a war surgeon.

627
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:51,960
Really?

628
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:55,160
Then did you see a real war?

629
00:41:59,560 --> 00:42:01,220
You will as well in the future.

630
00:42:02,080 --> 00:42:02,880
In the future,

631
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:05,040
people all over China may see

632
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:06,570
the war with their own eyes.

633
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:13,360
Thank you.

634
00:42:15,440 --> 00:42:16,240
Not a big deal.

635
00:42:26,480 --> 00:42:27,400
It's going to rain.

636
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:28,400
Let's go back now.

637
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,720
Your wound needs to be treated, too.

638
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:32,880
Come here.

639
00:42:39,600 --> 00:42:40,200
Stand up.

640
00:42:45,240 --> 00:42:45,800
Let's go.

641
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:51,920
I'll carry you.

642
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:52,480
Come on.

643
00:42:53,080 --> 00:42:53,640
Quickly.
